def filter_and_sum(df, column):
    df = df.dropna(subset=[column])
    df = df[df['Age'] >= 20]
    df = df[df['Name'].str.isalpha()]
    df = df[df['Gender'].isin(['Male', 'Female'])]
    df = df[df['Nationality'].isin(['USA', 'Canada'])]
    sum_salary = df['Salary'].sum()
    return sum_salary
